Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.13,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's… the ponies from my old village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.87,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,With my past, I should never be in charge of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:17.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,They've taken my sister and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.38,Luna,,0,0,0,,It's worse than the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis and the changelings are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:24.82,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,They ponynapped all of the most powerful ponies in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.63,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This is Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He's a reformed changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,They took Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:34.76,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I think I have a pretty good idea where she might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:23.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is so strange. We're here and that's there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:27.18,Discord,,0,0,0,,and I clearly meant for us to be there and not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.51,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can probably explain…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.24,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh well, if at first you don't succeed…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should come up with a plan first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:36.94,Discord,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:42.05,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You know, figuring out the best way to do something before you actually do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,That's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:47.73,Discord,,0,0,0,,But you see unlike you I can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:48.61,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:51.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,That's all very nice but really waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:55.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,We have me and what else could we possibly need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,A draconequus with magic and half a brain might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why are you here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:06.68,Discord,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like you're going to stop the changelings by pulling a rabbit out of the hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:09.72,Discord,,0,0,0,,At least, my magic can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.50,Thorax,,0,0,0,,The thing about magic here is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.23,Discord,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:15.11,Discord,,0,0,0,,For Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.26,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to tell you:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:27.12,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Nothing other than changeling magic works here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:30.49,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Chrisalis's throne is carved from an ancient dark stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:34.42,Thorax,,0,0,0,,that soaks up outside magic the same way changelings soak up love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.36,Thorax,,0,0,0,,It's how she keeps the hive safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.70,Trixie,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.49,Trixie,,0,0,0,,what kind of plan were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.90,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Without magic, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But nopony else is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.30,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,so somepony better come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:55.63,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Anypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.30,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:01.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This throne…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If we get into the hive and destroy it…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Can we get our magic back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.19,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.97,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a terrible plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,How all we even supposed to get into the hive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.74,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:18.18,Discord,,0,0,0,,I haven't walked that far in a millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,I don't know how any of you manage not being able
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:30.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,to disappear and reappear whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:34.71,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, I for one definitely miss you being able to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Give Discord a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,None of us knew weren't going to be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.01,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:46.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If we get separated, it might make sense to have a way to make sure we are who we say we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,Like a secret code!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:53.08,Discord,,0,0,0,,How about, if I say, "We are…", and you say "doomed".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,Or you say "Rescue" and I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:01.78,Trixie,,0,0,0,,How about that we say "Klutzy" and you say "Draconequus".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.68,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Klutzy draqonequus… Works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.47,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.49,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm definitely glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I don't think we'd be able to find our way without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.47,Thorax,,0,0,0,,You definitely wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Where is the way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.11,Thorax,,0,0,0,,It's a changeling hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.20,Thorax,,0,0,0,,It shifts and changes like we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.23,Thorax,,0,0,0,,And we're the only ones to who can navigate in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:39.62,Thorax,,0,0,0,,It's total chaos to not changelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:44.19,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a decent chaos, I don't know if I'd call it "total".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:50.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,Are we sure that I'll get my magic back when we destroy this throne thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If Thorax is right, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.18,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, that's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.45,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And how are we supposed to destroy that throne when we find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.82,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you brought any throne-destroying tools
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.68,Discord,,0,0,0,,along with these useless sideshow props.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:17.95,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Asks the lord of chaos, who can't go for a walk without whining nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.20,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, but when the throne is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:24.95,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to rip the very fabric of reality to save our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:30.73,Discord,,0,0,0,,While you'll still be self-absorbed, the below average… illusionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.63,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Self-absorbed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:33.78,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.02,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Cut. It. Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm just barely keeping it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:40.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And it would be wonderful if you two could actually try to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:42.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,instead of bickering like a fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.61,Trixie,,0,0,0,,How can we help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:52.09,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Don't asked me, I couldn't even handle giving advice at the Sunset Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.98,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And I had magic then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.40,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And the three of us are as good as useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.82,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,At least, Thorax knows where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.68,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.52,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I think we're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.31,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:10.15,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We might as well just sit here and wait for the changelings to soak up all of our love or
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.74,Trixie,,0,0,0,,whatever gross thing it is that they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.40,Trixie,,0,0,0,,How often do you all get hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:19.43,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Actually, I haven't been since I met Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.70,Thorax,,0,0,0,,And changelings are always hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.76,Thorax,,0,0,0,,We can never get enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.74,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just superb…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.63,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But, you aren't hungry at all now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.13,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Once I made a few friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.88,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I guess I just sort of forgot about the whole feeding thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.54,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Is that about the same time your wings changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.50,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:46.73,Discord,,0,0,0,,While I would love to sit around chitchatting about feeding and not feeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:50.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,I have a Fluttershy to save!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.22,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Can you please lower you voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.21,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You gonna get us all captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, you keep saying that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:05.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,but I haven't seen an actual changeling since we got into this hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.47,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.48,Thorax,,0,0,0,,A changeling patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:23.98,Discord,,0,0,0,,This seems like one of those moments where we need a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.53,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What kind of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:29.37,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We have no magic, and it's not like my illusions are gonna save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.74,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Do you have any of your smoke bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.85,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Looking for somepony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.38,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Is that the best you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.69,Discord,,0,0,0,,Not exactly great and powerful, but effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.18,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Klutzy…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.65,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Draconequus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.65,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Draconequus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:10.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,I really think we need a new codeword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.71,Thorax,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.09,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But we still don't know where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Actually, we might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Two of the changelings didn't go with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:22.95,Thorax,,0,0,0,,With an intruder in the hive, they went to protect the queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.03,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.16,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We… go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:47.58,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Even if I wanted to, there's no way past the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.31,Thorax,,0,0,0,,We'll be spotted for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We need some kind of… distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'm fresh out of smoke bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.60,Discord,,0,0,0,,Normally, I'm the most distracting thing I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,But without magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.02,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:11.48,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hello, changelings and changelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.69,Discord,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I was just as surprised as you are, that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:17.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,When I heard that I'll be playing for a bunch of changelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.79,Discord,,0,0,0,,I was beside myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,Then I realised it was just one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,But, seriously, this isn't the toughest crowd I've ever been in front of,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:31.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,but it's definitely the easiest to bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,To bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.28,Discord,,0,0,0,,Is this thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think that you can do any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.88,Discord,,0,0,0,,be my guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.05,Trixie,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely ridiculous that that worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.39,Discord,,0,0,0,,It is certainly a pleasure to have such dedicated fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:01.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,I have to come back with some new material after I rescue Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.96,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,You certainly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,And I should probably help you get free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.21,Discord,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,But you're obviously not Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:29.33,Discord,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm separated from a group and just happened to come across the one pony I care most about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.84,Discord,,0,0,0,,I can smell the set up a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No… You're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There's no way you should trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Just go find the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.74,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We're probably all changelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't rescue any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:11:00.35,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Unless… you think, maybe one of us might be the real Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:05.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, that certainly would be a nasty changeling trick, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm the real Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.04,Thorax,,0,0,0,,We can't wait for Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.09,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Between seeing him and Trixie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.74,Thorax,,0,0,0,,the castle will be crawling with guards soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:26.12,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But if we do manage to destroy Chrysalis's throne, we'll need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He could take on the entire changeling army by sneezing if he wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.28,Trixie,,0,0,0,,He's probably already been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.96,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fellow rescuers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.82,Thorax,,0,0,0,,We can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.38,Thorax,,0,0,0,,We gotta find the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.26,Discord,,0,0,0,,I heard some of the changelings who were chasing me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.46,Discord,,0,0,0,,say that they know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.43,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Klutzy…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.53,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can be klutzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.53,Discord,,0,0,0,,Now, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You know that's not Discord, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.49,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,This way, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.54,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I know this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.00,Thorax,,0,0,0,,If he says to go left,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.57,Thorax,,0,0,0,,we should definitely go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.12,Thorax,,0,0,0,,He's leading us to a swarm waiting to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.67,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.41,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You two just get ready to run into the other tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.38,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.83,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We've already lost Discord, I can't lose you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.14,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Without magic I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:32.73,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight, you've got us this far with just my illusions and Discord's annoying personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.72,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You don't need magic to figure out what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.19,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I know you are afraid to be in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,but you are really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Listen to your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.19,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Hey, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.55,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Wanna see the new trick I've been working on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.65,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I call it "The Changeling Capture"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.15,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.17,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Ta da!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:49.04,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,One little pony, all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:56.26,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Oh, how will I ever prevent this daring rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.83,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:13.53,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,The Princess of Friendship's sole pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:18.64,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I didn't think you were worth replacing with one of my drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.73,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:26.23,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Nopony is coming to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.96,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Your little squad was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.96,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,And now there is just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thorax is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.56,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Don't mention that traitor's name in my Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.99,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,He was a fool to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.32,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,And even more a fool to returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:45.02,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,When I find him, he'll learn just what happens to those
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.09,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,who betray the Hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:53.19,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,And it seems I don't have far to look, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.77,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Thorax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.21,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:11.11,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,And clearly Thorax revealed to you the secret of my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:15.76,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,I can't have powerful ponies using their abilities against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:20.01,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Even with your rather embarrassing little rescue attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.25,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Everything has gone according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What plan, why did you do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.61,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,So I can feed, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.27,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,By replacing the most beloved figures in Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:36.18,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,my drones will be able to store all the love meant for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.60,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,and return it here, to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.93,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Everypony will do as I command!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:46.86,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,And my subjects and I will feed on their love for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.67,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What if you didn't have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.14,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:01.33,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,The hunger of changelings can never be satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thorax left the Hive and made a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He shared love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And now he doesn't need to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:12.48,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You don't have to live your life starving all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:18.20,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,You know nothing of the changelings or what it takes to be their Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:24.17,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,I decide what is best for my subjects, not some mewling grub!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:28.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know what it's like to lead by fear and intimidation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:32.21,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and I know what it's like to want everypony to do what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:38.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,A real leader doesn't force her subjects to deny who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She celebrates what makes them unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.25,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And listens when one of them finds a better way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.44,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,The only thing Thorax has found
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.40,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,is what happens to those who turned their back on the Hive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:57.64,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Just as soon as I drain every last ounce of love from him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.04,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,and show my subjects what a real leader is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.99,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I can feel the love inside me slipping away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.14,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I can't hold on to it much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Then don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:13.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sharing love is what made you different to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You should share yours with Chrysalis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Give her all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:42.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when you give love freely instead of taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's… good to see you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:31.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We defeated the changelings with no magic at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,they found a new leader, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:36.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,they're all… kind of good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.33,Luna,,0,0,0,,Well done, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.49,Luna,,0,0,0,,It seems as though you've learned a great deal since we last spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.30,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,When Twilight and her friends defeated me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I chose to run away and seek revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.95,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You can be the leader your subjects deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.33,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,There is no revenge you could ever conceive of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:18.50,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,that will come close to what I exact upon you one day, Starlight Glimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.80,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Thorax, as the new leader of the changelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:34.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I look forward to discussing how we can improve our relationship in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:40.95,Celestia,,0,0,0,,However, for the moment, perhaps it is best that we leave the Changeling Kingdom to the changelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,Splendid idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:48.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,Now, who's ready for some celebratory tea at Fluttershy's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:57.25,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Actually, now that you can snap your claws and send us absolutely anywhere again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think I have a better option.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:04.84,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,Hey, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.41,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.79,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,You left in such a hurry before…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.13,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,we kinda thought you didn't wanna come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.54,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I guess after the way I used my magic on all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:19.33,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure I was somepony who should even be in charge of a baking contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:22.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I was afraid I might go back to being a pony I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:27.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But, I realized that sometimes you don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You have to step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.82,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And I have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:33.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can handle it, whether it means saving Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.48,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,or helping friends with the Sunset Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.56,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.61,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know the festival's almost over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:44.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but I kinda invited a few of my friends to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Hope that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.01,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Great. Now where's that baking contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.61,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This pony needs a cupcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm able to rip the very fabric of reality again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:10.55,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And I'm still a self-absorbed, below-averaged illusionist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:15.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was going to say a couple of those illusions were slightly above average.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:19.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,If you ever need a little chaos in your act, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:23.03,Trixie,,0,0,0,,When pigs fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.20,Discord,,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:36.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Somepony is really gonna have to catch us up on what we've missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.71,Auto,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONEC
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.26,Auto,,0,0,0,,anon2anon\Nsunnysubs.com